  9→                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none">
 10→                    <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
 11→                </svg>
